column2: SELECT count (*) FROM (SELECT f.specobjid, f.petromag_g, (SELECT MIN (p.petromag_g) FROM dbo.fGetNearbyObjEq (f.ra, f.dec, #*f.petroR5#_r) n JOIN photoprimary p ON p.objid = n.objid WHERE n.objid < > f.objid) AS BrightestObjin1#R5# FROM (SELECT s.specobjid, SL.ew as EW_Ha, p.objid, p.ra, p.dec, p.petroR5#_g, p.petromag_g FROM photoprimary p JOIN specobj s ON p.objid = s.bestobjid JOIN SpecLine SL ON s.specobjid = SL.specobjid WHERE s.z > # AND petroR5#_r > # AND petroR5#_g > # AND (p.petroMag_g + p.extinction_g - #*log1# (#*s.z) ) > (#* (p.petroMag_g + p.extinction_g - p.petroMag_r - p.extinction_r) - #) AND (p.petroMag_g + p.extinction_g + #*log1# (p.petroR5#_g) - p.petroMag_r - p.extinction_r - #*log1# (p.petroR5#_r) ) < = # AND (# + p.petroMag_g + p.extinction_g + #*log1# (p.petroR5#_g) ) < (# - #* (p.petroMag_g + p.extinction_g - p.petroMag_r + p.extinction_r + #*log1# (p.petroR5#_g) - #*log1# (p.petroR5#_r) )) AND SL.lineID = # AND SL.ew > #) f JOIN SpecLine SL ON f.specobjid = SL.specobjid WHERE SL.lineID = # AND Log1# (SL.ew/f.EW_Ha) < #) g WHERE petromag_g > (BrightestObjin1#R5# - #)
